                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Actually I've found that if you add our lowest scent line spell to your lineup and cast it once every 20 - 30 seconds it will give you enough aggro to still use your pet hasted.  Has worked for me in PoV/PoS, PoD (Guardians), PoN wraiths/banshees & gargoyles.<br /><br />Alot of the mobs resist the scent spell, but that's okay, it still seems to throw alot of aggro in there.<br /><br />I have taken splurt and pyro out of my lineup for the time being as well, unless I just want to sit/swap for them after having casted CoC/Ebolt on the mob.  It takes a substantial more amount of mana, but it's manageable right now.  If you were always killing with no downtime before, expect to have downtime after 5 or so kills now.<br /><br />Craigmandu<br />62 Warlock<br />On Tarrew Marr</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
